Class NucleotidePointLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.hgvs.nts.NucleotidePointLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConvertibleToHGVSString

    public class NucleotidePointLocation
extends Object
implements ConvertibleToHGVSString
    Position in a nucleotide string. Characterized by a 1-based position in the current coordinate system (e.g. CDS) with an offset into the exon/intron.
    Author:
    Manuel Holtgrewe
